I"¦<blockquote>
  <p><em>Manage &gt; System &gt; Advanced settings</em></p>
</blockquote>

<p>Set <code class="highlighter-rouge">VMkernel.Boot.disableACSCheck</code> to <code class="highlighter-rouge">True</code>.</p>

